ISO base media file format viewer.
----------------------------------

 $ ./showboxes.py yourfile.mp4

The definitions of structures can be found in the publicly available
standard ISO/IEC 14496-12 (ISO base media file format).

Download link for the lazy:
http://standards.iso.org/ittf/PubliclyAvailableStandards/index.html

For more info, contact the author at amarghosh at gmail dot com

